            <lg xml:id="TK147">
<l>aṟaṉiyalā ṉilvāḻvā ṉeṉpāṉ piṟaṉiyalāḷ</l>
<l>peṇmai nayavā tavaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is known as a householder in accord with dharma, who does not crave</l>
<l>the womanhood of her who's in accord with another.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
